      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle exhibits impeccable cosmetic and mechanical integrity, reflective of its showroom-floor origins. Every detail has been curated to satisfy the most discerning collector. Experience uncompromised performance and luxury in a vehicle that transcends the standard pre-owned market.",
