      "description": "We are proud to present this superlative vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. Offered in immaculate condition, this specimen represents a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to acquire a vehicle that remains in showroom state. Every detail, from the flawless exterior to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a history of meticulous care and climate-controlled storage. This automobile performs with the precision and grace of a new machine, standing as a testament to its peerless provenance and mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 45800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
